WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Welcome back to High Stakes Poker. Let's deal a new hand.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Hand number 1. Phil Hellmuth is on the button with pocket aces.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Hellmuth raises to 3,000. Tom Dwan in the big blind calls with king queen suited.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
The flop comes ace of hearts, seven of clubs, two of diamonds.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Dwan checks. Hellmuth bets 4,000. Dwan folds.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Hand number 2. Daniel Negreanu raises to 2,500 from under the gun.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Phil Hellmuth three bets to 8,000 from the cutoff. Negreanu calls.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:40.000
The flop is king of spades, jack of hearts, ten of clubs. Negreanu checks.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:45.000
Hellmuth bets 12,000. Negreanu raises to 35,000. Hellmuth folds.
